  <strong><h1><font size="30">Hibiscus </font> </h1></strong>

<strong>
Hibiscus, also known as hibiscus flowers, refused to frosting,
magnolia, to Hibiscus, China wood, native to China. Prefer warm,
moist environment, not cold. Avoid drought, water wet. Less demanding
of soil and barren land can grow. The case of the Malvaceae, Hibiscus.
Deciduous shrub or small tree. A profusion of high-only 1m Xu. 
Shaped leaf, wide oval, was 3 to 5 cleft, the lobes triangular, base cordate,
leaf margin with blunt teeth, coat both sides. Spent on the branch side axillary solitary.
9 November opening sequence. Flowers, leaves can be medicine, detoxification, swelling and pus,
cooling blood to stop bleeding effect.
   </strong>
